Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: The redacted package provides a set of utility functions for 
  redacting and masking sensitive information in text data. This includes 
  functions for redacting passwords, API keys, and other sensitive information 
  using regular expressions, as well as a utility function for general pattern 
  matching and replacement.
